.TH "mipi_dsi_dcs_get_power_mode" 9 "mipi_dsi_dcs_get_power_mode" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
mipi_dsi_dcs_get_power_mode \- query the display module's current power mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" mipi_dsi_dcs_get_power_mode
.BI "(struct mipi_dsi_device *dsi "  ","
.BI "u8 *mode "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dsi" 12
DSI peripheral device
.IP "mode" 12
return location for the current power mode
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success or a negative error code on failure.
